sys_remote_update_set.description:
This template emphasizes a clean, modern, and neutral design that can be tailored to fit a wide variety of company brands.
Installation instructions: 1. Install the following plugins: Floor Plan Viewer, Facilities Service Automation, Human Resources Service Automation: Core, Human Resources Service Automation: Employee Change, Chat. Include demo data where possible.
2. Load the Bootstrap Carousel Update Set found on Share (https://share.servicenow.com/app.do#/detailV2/dc03da922b9fa1004a1e976be8da15c5/overview).
3. Load this update set.
To change the portal URL: Go to Content Management > Sites > Branded CMS. Update the URL suffix field.
To change the home page title: Go to Content Management > Pages > Branded CMS. Update the Title field.
To change the footer contents: Go to Content Management > Dynamic > Branded CMS Footer. Update the text.
To change the main logo: Go to Content Management > Headers > Branded CMS Header. Update the Logo field with your own image.
To turn off chat links: Go to Content Management > Navigation Menus > Branded CMS Global Menu. Click on the "Chat By Department" Menu Item. Uncheck the Active field and save.
To change the scrolling banner images: Go to Content Management > Bootstrap Carousels > Branded CMS Home Carousel. Here you can edit or create new slides. Click into any of the carousel slides and edit their content, as well as update the images they may be referencing as their background image. To replace the existing images, go to Content Management > Images, and replace branded-cms-banner-1.jpg, branded-cms-banner-2.jpg, and branded-cms-banner-3.jpg. You can also upload your own images here and reference them in your slides. For optimal viewing, please use an image that is at least 1140 pixels wide and 500 pixels tall (300 pixels tall for the HR CMS).
Tested in Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and IE10+

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_block_programmatic"><content_block_programmatic action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><category>general</category><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><frame/><logged_on>false</logged_on><name>Branded CMS Knowledge Base</name><programmatic_content><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">

<g:evaluate jelly="true">
	var kbSysId = RP.getParameterValue( 'kb' ),
		iframe = new GlideRecord( 'content_block_iframe' ),
	url = '$knowledge.do#/search?kb=';

	if ( !!kbSysId ) {
		url += kbSysId;
	}

	iframe.initialize();
	iframe.frame_name = 'knowledge_frame';
	iframe.url = url;
	iframe.sizing = 'expand';
	iframe.putCurrent();
</g:evaluate>
<g:render_content_block_iframe />
<g:evaluate>
	iframe.popCurrent();
</g:evaluate>

</j:jelly>
]]></programmatic_content><sys_class_name>content_block_programmatic</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>kai.yao</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-03-04 20:49:21</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>041a23de4f227100c163e321a310c7d1</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Knowledge Base</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_block_programmatic_041a23de4f227100c163e321a310c7d1</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-30 10:19:12</sys_updated_on><two_phase>false</two_phase></content_block_programmatic></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS Layout Styles (Mobile)</name><style>/* Mobile + Default Styles */

.page-title, .branded-admin-nav, #page_timing_div { display: none; }

/* Admin Bar */
.branded-admin-nav { z-index: 0; }
.navbar-inverse .navbar-brand:hover,
.navbar-inverse .navbar-brand:focus { color: #9d9d9d; }

/* Header */
.cms_header { padding-bottom: 20px; }

.cms_menu_super_menu_content {
	display: none;
	position: absolute;
	padding: 10px 15px;
	text-align: left;
	background: #fff;
	border: 1px solid #666;
	z-index: 1;
}

td.cms_header_top_menu { height: 40px; padding-bottom: 20px; line-height: 40px; }

.cms_header span.globalSearch { display: block; padding: 5px; margin-top: 5px; line-height: 20px; border: 1px solid #ccc; }
.cms_header span.globalSearch #sysparm_search { margin-left: 5px; width: 93%; }
.cms_header_login_link { text-align: right; }

.cms_header_resizer_link:last-child { margin-left: 10px; }

td.cms_header_logo, td.cms_header_text { display: block; }
div.cms_header_text { display: none; }

.cms_header_bottom_menu { position: relative; padding-top: 10px; }
.cms_header_bottom_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item,
.cms_header_bottom_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item_selected { float: left; }
.cms_header_bottom_menu .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2 { margin: 0; line-height: 30px; }
.cms_header_bottom_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item:first-child .menu_section,
.cms_header_bottom_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item_selected:first-child .menu_section { padding-left: 0; }
.cms_header_bottom_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_bar .menu_section {
	display: block;
	padding: 0 15px;
	font-size: 20px;
	letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	line-height: 1.5;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

.cms_header_bottom_menu .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2,
.branded-chat-container {
	font-size: 16px;
	font-weight: 400;
	letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	vertical-align: middle;
}
.branded-chat-container { float: right; min-width: 280px; line-height: 60px; }
.branded-chat-avatar { float:right; margin-left: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
.branded-chat-container .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2 { display: none; }
.branded-chat-container .cms_menu_super_menu_content { min-width: 300px; }
.branded-chat-container > div { line-height: 60px; }
.branded-chat-department { line-height: 30px; }
.branded-icon-chat { margin-top: -2px; }
.branded-chat-link { margin-left: 5px; }

/* Home Page */
.page-home .carousel { display: none; }
.branded-cms-home-menu a { color: #fff; }
.branded-cms-home-menu .branded-horizontal-block-content {
	margin-bottom: 20px;
	color: #fff;
	-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
	-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
	background: #111;
	background: rgba( 0, 0, 0, 0.8 );
}
/*.branded-cms-home-menu .branded-horizontal-block:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }*/

/* Home Pages */
.branded-horizontal-block-header::after { display: table; content: ''; clear: both; }
.branded-horizontal-block-icon-container,
.branded-horizontal-block-text { float: left; }
.branded-horizontal-block-icon-container { padding-left: 10px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks { display: none !important; }
.main-content .row .cms_menu_section_blocks { display: block !important; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_image_left,
.branded-horizontal-block-icon { width: 90px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title,
.branded-horizontal-block-text { padding-left: 15px; }
.branded-horizontal-block-text { padding-top: 23px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2,
.branded-horizontal-block-title {
	margin: 0;
	font-size: 18px;
	font-weight: 400;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_second_level_text,
.branded-horizontal-block-subtitle { letter-spacing: 0.05em; font-size: 12px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_separator { display: none; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .main-content-menu-block-items { padding: 20px 0 40px 100px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .main-content-menu-block-items td { padding-bottom: 10px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .main-content-menu-block-items tr:last-child td { padding-bottom: 0; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .menu_bullet { min-width: 20px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_block_item {
	display: block;
	margin-left: 10px;
	font-size: 18px;
}

.main-content .cms_menu_vertical_block .cms_menu_vertical_blocks_image_left { width: 90px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_vertical_block td.cms_menu_vertical_blocks_title { padding-left: 20px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_vertical_block .cms_menu_vertical_blocks_title h2 {
	margin: 0;
	font-size: 22px;
	font-weight: 400;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Typeahead Search Bar */
.typeahead-search { margin: 0; }
.typeahead-search .input-group-btn { display: table-cell !important; }
.typeahead-search .twitter-typeahead { display: table-cell !important; width: 100%; }
.typeahead-search .typeahead-search-text {
	box-sizing: border-box;
	width: 100%;
	padding: 5px 30px 5px 10px;
	font-size: 16px;
	background: url( 'images/search_glass.gifx' ) no-repeat scroll 99% 8px;
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	z-index: 0;
}
.typeahead-search-submit { visibility: hidden; width: 1px; height: 1px; position: absolute; top: -9999px; }

.tt-dropdown-menu {
	width: 100%;
	max-height: 250px;
	overflow-y: auto;
	box-sizing: border-box;
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	font-size: 16px;
	background: #fff;
}
.tt-suggestion { padding: 10px; }
.typeahead-search-noresults { padding: 10px; width: 100%; color: #4c4c4c; }
.typeahead-search-suggestion-title {
	margin: 0;
	color: #4c4c4c;
	font-size: 16px;
	font-weight: normal;
	line-height: 1.2;
}
.typeahead-search-suggestion-text {
	overflow: hidden;
	margin: 0;
	color: #999;
	font-size: 14px;
	font-weight: 300;
	line-height: 1.5;
	text-overflow: ellipsis;
	max-height: 37px;
}

.tt-suggestion.tt-cursor { background: #278EFC; }
.tt-suggestion.tt-cursor .typeahead-search-suggestion-title { color: #fff; }
.tt-suggestion.tt-cursor .typeahead-search-suggestion-text { color: #fff; }

/* Iframe pages */
iframe { transform: translate3d(0,0,0); transition: height 500ms; }

.branded-page-title {
	margin: 20px 0 20px;
	font-size: 24px;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	line-height: 1;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}
#catalog_frame, #support_frame { margin-top: 20px; }

/* Get Help + Catalog */
.page-get_help .main-content > .row,
.page-requestsomething .main-content > .row { display: none; }

.page-get_help .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title { padding-left: 5px; }
.branded-gethelp-selection-container,
.branded-catalog-selection-container { margin: 20px 0 10px; }
.branded-gethelp-label,
.branded-catalog-label { margin-right: 15px; }
.branded-gethelp-selection-container .btn-group,
.branded-catalog-selection-container .btn-group { display: inline-block !important; }
.branded-gethelp-selection-container .caret,
.branded-catalog-selection-container .caret { position: absolute; top: 15px; right: 15px; }
.branded-gethelp-selection-container .branded-gethelp-dropdown,
.branded-catalog-selection-container .branded-catalog-dropdown { width: 100%; }
.branded-gethelp-selection-container .branded-gethelp-dropdown-button,
.branded-catalog-selection-container .branded-catalog-dropdown-button {
	position: relative;
	width: 210px;
	padding: 5px 15px;
	text-align: left;
}
.branded-gethelp-selection-container .branded-gethelp-dropdown-button:hover,
.branded-catalog-selection-container .branded-catalog-dropdown-button:hover { box-shadow: none; }

/* knowledge/catalog */
.branded-main-container { padding-top: 40px; }
.branded-section-title {
	margin: 0;
	font-size: 18px;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Catalog styles */
.page-requestsomething .main-content > .row { display: none; }

/* My Requests */
.branded-service-requests-title { margin-top: 40px; }

/* Footer */
.branded-footer {
	margin-top: 40px;
	padding-top: 40px;
	padding-bottom: 40px;
	font-size: 12px;
	font-weight: 500;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
}
.branded-footer-left,
.branded-footer-right { text-align: center; }
</style><sys_class_name>content_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-21 08:55:40</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>152c224d4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e72</sys_id><sys_mod_count>222</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Layout Styles (Mobile)</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_css_152c224d4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e72</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-23 10:42:10</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS Bootstrap Overrides</name><style>/* Concessions made to Bootstrap Styles because of ServiceNow's layout engine. */

/* Fade Carousel */
.carousel .carousel-inner .item { display: block; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.5s; }
.carousel .carousel-inner .active { opacity: 1; }
.carousel .carousel-inner .left,
.carousel .carousel-inner .right { left: 0; }
.carousel .carousel-inner > .item.prev,
.carousel .carousel-inner > .item.active.left { transform: none; -webkit-transform: none; }

/* Margins for columns have to be changed for table cells (margins don't affect them) */
td.row > table > thead > tr > th[class*="col-"]:first-child,
td.row > table > tbody > tr > td[class*="col-"]:first-child,
td.row > div[class*="col-"]:first-child {
	padding-left: 0;
}

td.row > table > thead > tr > th[class*="col-"]:last-child,
td.row > table > tbody > tr > td[class*="col-"]:last-child,
td.row > div[class*="col-"]:last-child {
	padding-right: 0;
}</style><sys_class_name>content_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-23 02:25:43</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>b985af214dec310062c55dc1f2a64e86</sys_id><sys_mod_count>14</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Bootstrap Overrides</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_css_b985af214dec310062c55dc1f2a64e86</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-02-18 14:31:19</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Used on the Knowledgebase page on the Branded CMS Template</description><global>false</global><name>branded-knowledgebase</name><script><![CDATA[// used for the Branded v2 Search/Article page

define( [ 'jquery' ], function( $j ) {
'use strict';

var iframe = document.getElementById( 'knowledge_frame' ),
	$iframe = $j( iframe ),
	$kbDoc = $j( iframe.contentDocument ),

	updateLayout = function() {
		var $kbContainer;

		$kbDoc = $j( $iframe[ 0 ].contentDocument );
		$kbContainer = $kbDoc.find( '.application' );

		// re-doing the bootstrap rows and columns
		$kbContainer.removeClass( 'container-fluid' ).addClass( 'row' );
		$kbContainer.children( '.ng-scope' ).addClass( 'container-fluid' );
		$kbContainer.find( '.search-bar .col-xs-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12' ).removeClass( 'col-xs-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12' );
	};

$kbDoc.ready( function() {
	$iframe.on( 'load', function() { setTimeout( updateLayout, 800 ); } );

	setTimeout( updateLayout, 800 );
} );

} );
]]></script><script_name/><sys_class_name>sys_ui_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>kai.yao</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-03-04 21:50:54</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>bd49fb924f627100c163e321a310c7fa</sys_id><sys_mod_count>26</sys_mod_count><sys_name>branded-knowledgebase</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ui_script_bd49fb924f627100c163e321a310c7fa</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-13 07:36:27</sys_updated_on><use_scoped_format>false</use_scoped_format></sys_ui_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ui_script_f4abb5a79b0231003fe61c76065498d9
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Scripts used for the Branded CMS' "Report An Issue" page.</description><global>false</global><name>branded-get-help</name><script><![CDATA[define( [ 'jquery', 'underscore', 'backbone' ], function( $j, _, Backbone ) {
'use strict';

var menuIndexMap = {
		'it'         : 0,
		'facilities' : 1,
		'finance'    : 2,
		'hr'         : 3,
		'legal'      : 4,
		'marketing'  : 5
	};

var selectViewCore = {
		el : '.branded-gethelp-dropdown',

		events : {
			'click .branded-gethelp-dropdown-link' : 'loadDepartment'
		},

		firstLoadDepartment : function() {
			// for when the page loads and we load the initial page config

			var $menus = $j( '.page-get_help .main-content > .row' ),
				$iframe = $j( '#support_frame' ),
				department = ( typeof brandedGethelpDepartment !== 'undefined' ) ? brandedGethelpDepartment : 'it', // determined in the gethelp-select dynamic block
				$departmentMenu = $j( $menus[ menuIndexMap[ department ] ] );

			$menus.hide();
			$departmentMenu.show();
		},

		loadDepartment : function( ev ) {
			var $menus = $j( '.page-get_help .main-content > .row' ),
				$dropdownButton = this.$el.parent().find( '.branded-gethelp-dropdown-button' ),
				$dropdownButtonText = this.$el.parent().find( '.branded-gethelp-dropdown-button-text' ),
				$iframe = $j( '#support_frame' ),
				$target = this.$el.find( ev.currentTarget ),
				department = $target.data( 'department' ),
				$departmentMenu;

			// Do nothing if the user selects the same department as the active department
			$dropdownButtonText.empty().append( $target.html() );

			if ( $dropdownButton.data( 'active' ) === $target.data( 'department' ) ) {
				return;
			}

			$dropdownButton.data( 'active', $target.data( 'department' ) );
			$departmentMenu = $j( $menus[ menuIndexMap[ department ] ] );

			$menus.hide();
			$departmentMenu.show();

			$iframe[ 0 ].src = $departmentMenu.find( 'a' ).first().attr( 'href' );
		}
	};

var selectView = new ( Backbone.View.extend( selectViewCore ) )();

$j( document ).ready( function() {
	selectView.firstLoadDepartment();
} );

} );
]]></script><script_name/><sys_class_name>sys_ui_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-02-11 13:23:08</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>f4abb5a79b0231003fe61c76065498d9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>29</sys_mod_count><sys_name>branded-get-help</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ui_script_f4abb5a79b0231003fe61c76065498d9</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-30 12:23:08</sys_updated_on><use_scoped_format>false</use_scoped_format></sys_ui_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS Layout Styles (Small Screens)</name><style>@media ( min-width: 768px ) {
	div.cms_header_search, .cms_header_font_size, .cms_header_login, div.cms_header_top_menu { float: right; padding: 0 15px; text-align: center; }

	div.cms_header_top_menu,
	td.cms_header_text { position: relative !important; }

	.cms_header span.globalSearch #sysparm_search { margin-right: 5%; }

	.page-home .carousel { display: block; margin-bottom: 40px; }
	.page-home .carousel-inner,
	.page-home .carousel-inner > .item { height: 310px; }
	.page-home .carousel-inner > .item { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; }
	.page-home .carousel-control,
	.page-home .carousel-indicators { display: none; }
	.page-home .carousel-caption {
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 0;
		text-shadow: 0 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
		padding: 20px 40px;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}
	.page-home .carousel-caption h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 500;
		-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
		-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
	}
	.page-home .carousel-caption p { display: none; }
}</style><sys_class_name>content_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-24 15:24:15</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>bad1e38e4d60710062c55dc1f2a64e0d</sys_id><sys_mod_count>43</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Layout Styles (Small Screens)</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_css_bad1e38e4d60710062c55dc1f2a64e0d</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-06 22:06:11</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ui_script_203710a84f2e7100ce7522788310c72d
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Drives the UI for the Catalog page in the Branded CMS Template.</description><global>false</global><name>branded-catalog</name><script><![CDATA[define( [ 'jquery', 'underscore', 'backbone' ], function( $j, _, Backbone ) {
'use strict';

var iframe = document.getElementById( 'catalog_frame' ),
	$iframe = $j( iframe ),
	menuIndexMap = {
		'it'         : 0,
		'facilities' : 1,
		'finance'    : 2,
		'hr'         : 3,
		'legal'      : 4,
		'marketing'  : 5
	},

	styleIframe = function() {
		var $iframeDoc = $j( iframe.contentDocument );

		// add overriding styles to iframe
		$iframeDoc.find( 'head' ).append( '<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/d7fafb024da0710062c55dc1f2a64ee3.cssdbx" />' );
	},

	updateLayout = function() {
		var $iframeDoc = $j( iframe.contentDocument ),
			$iframeBody = $iframeDoc.find( 'body' );


	},

	selectViewCore = {
		el : '.branded-catalog-dropdown',

		events : {
			'click .branded-catalog-dropdown-link' : 'loadCatalog'
		},

		redirectIframe : function( $catalogMenu ) {
			iframe.src = $catalogMenu.find( 'a' ).first().attr( 'href' );
			$j( iframe.contentDocument ).ready( this.setupIframePage );
		},

		setupIframePage : function() {
			setTimeout( styleIframe, 800 );
		},

		firstLoadCatalogMenu : function() {
			// for when the page loads and we load the initial page config

			var $menus = $j( '.page-requestsomething .main-content > .row' ),
				catalog = ( typeof brandedCatalog !== 'undefined' && menuIndexMap[ brandedCatalog ] ) ? brandedCatalog : 'it', // determined in the catalog-select dynamic block
				$catalogMenu = $j( $menus[ menuIndexMap[ catalog ] ] );

			$menus.hide();
			$catalogMenu.show();

			if ( !$catalogMenu.find( 'a' ).first().attr( 'href' ) ) {
				console.log( $catalogMenu );
			}
		},

		loadCatalog : function( ev ) {
			var $menus = $j( '.page-requestsomething .main-content > .row' ),
				$dropdownButton = this.$el.parent().find( '.branded-catalog-dropdown-button' ),
				$dropdownButtonText = this.$el.parent().find( '.branded-catalog-dropdown-button-text' ),
				$target = this.$el.find( ev.currentTarget ),
				catalog = $target.data( 'catalog' ),
				$catalogMenu;

			// Do nothing if the user selects the same catalog as the active catalog
			$dropdownButtonText.empty().append( $target.html() );

			if ( $dropdownButton.data( 'active' ) === $target.data( 'catalog' ) ) {
				return;
			}

			$dropdownButton.data( 'active', $target.data( 'catalog' ) );
			$catalogMenu = $j( $menus[ menuIndexMap[ catalog ] ] );

			$menus.hide();
			$catalogMenu.show();

			this.redirectIframe( $catalogMenu );
		}
	},

	selectView = new ( Backbone.View.extend( selectViewCore ) )();

$j( document ).ready( function() {
	selectView.firstLoadCatalogMenu();

	$iframe.on( 'load', selectView.setupIframePage );
} );

} );
]]></script><script_name/><sys_class_name>sys_ui_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>kai.yao</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-02-26 18:53:54</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>203710a84f2e7100ce7522788310c72d</sys_id><sys_mod_count>63</sys_mod_count><sys_name>branded-catalog</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ui_script_203710a84f2e7100ce7522788310c72d</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-30 12:12:30</sys_updated_on><use_scoped_format>false</use_scoped_format></sys_ui_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: content_block_programmatic_40eb5b669b0331003fe61c7606549887
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_block_programmatic"><content_block_programmatic action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><category>general</category><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><frame/><logged_on>false</logged_on><name>Branded CMS Request Something IFrame Loader</name><programmatic_content><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">

<g:evaluate jelly="true">
	var catalog = RP.getParameterValue( 'catalog' ).toLowerCase(),
		menuGr = new GlideRecord( 'menu_section' ),
		catalogFrame = new GlideRecord( 'content_block_iframe' ),
		catalogIdMap = [
			{ catalog : 'it', sysId : '11e20e664d24710062c55dc1f2a64eee' },
			{ catalog : 'facilities', sysId : '670b5af74dac710062c55dc1f2a64e2b' },
			{ catalog : 'finance', sysId : 'f72ec5664fa27100c163e321a310c77c' },
			{ catalog : 'hr', sysId : '6ffca67b4dac710062c55dc1f2a64e75' },
			{ catalog : 'legal', sysId : '7bcc435a4f227100c163e321a310c764' },
			{ catalog : 'marketing', sysId : '5f181da64fa27100c163e321a310c7ed' }
		],
		catalogIds = [],
		catalogMenuUrls = {},
		catalogUrl,
		i;

	for ( i = 0; i < catalogIdMap.length; i++ ) {
		catalogIds.push( catalogIdMap[ i ].sysId );
	}

	menuGr.addQuery( 'content_block_menu', 'IN', catalogIds.join( ',' ) );
	menuGr.orderBy( 'order' );
	menuGr.query();

	while ( menuGr.next() ) {
		if ( typeof catalogMenuUrls[ menuGr.content_block_menu ] === 'undefined' ) {
			catalogMenuUrls[ menuGr.content_block_menu ] = new Array();
		}

		catalogMenuUrls[ menuGr.content_block_menu ].push( menuGr.url.toString() );
	}

	if ( catalog ) {
		for ( i = 0; i < catalogIdMap.length; i++ ) {
			if ( catalog == catalogIdMap[ i ].catalog ) {
				catalogUrl = catalogMenuUrls[ catalogIdMap[ i ].sysId ][ 0 ]
				i = catalogIdMap.length;
			}
		}
	} else {
		catalogUrl = catalogMenuUrls[ catalogIdMap[ 0 ].sysId ][ 0 ];
	}

	catalogFrame.initialize();
	catalogFrame.frame_name = 'catalog_frame';
	catalogFrame.url = catalogUrl;
	catalogFrame.sizing = 'expand';
	catalogFrame.putCurrent();
</g:evaluate>
<g:render_content_block_iframe />
<g:evaluate>
	catalogFrame.popCurrent();
</g:evaluate>

</j:jelly>
]]></programmatic_content><sys_class_name>content_block_programmatic</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-03-30 10:54:33</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>40eb5b669b0331003fe61c7606549887</sys_id><sys_mod_count>35</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Request Something IFrame Loader</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_block_programmatic_40eb5b669b0331003fe61c7606549887</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-30 12:01:18</sys_updated_on><two_phase>false</two_phase></content_block_programmatic></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS ServiceNow Overrides</name><style>/* Overriding default CMS/Iframed styles */
body { height: auto; margin: 0; }

table, input, select, button, input.text, textarea, input.button {
	font-size: inherit;
	font-family: inherit;
}

/* Disabling Heisenberg */
.modal-backdrop { z-index: 0; }

@media (min-width: 550px) {
	.container {
		width: auto;
	}
}

/* Iframed forms and lists */
html[data-doctype=true] body[data-formName="ui_page_render"] { margin: 0; }
html[data-doctype=true] div.section_header_content_no_scroll { overflow: visible; }
html[data-doctype=true] .list_nav.list_nav_top { background: transparent; }
.section_header_body_no_scroll { height: auto; max-height: none; }
.section_header_content_no_scroll { position: static !important; max-height: none; }
.section_header_div_no_scroll { position: static; }
tr.io_label td { background: transparent !important; }
div.form_title { font-size: 14px; }
.label { display: block; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; }
.label label { margin-bottom: 0; }
.list_nav.list_nav_top_border { position: static !important; border: 0 none; }
.list_nav_spacer { margin-top: 0 !important; }

.breadcrumb { padding: 0; background: transparent; }

/* Service Catalog */
#category_description, #navigatordetailTop, #back_cell, .header_bar_title { display: none !important; }
#goto_home { display: none; }

.sc_category_item .details_div td,
.sc_category_item_hover .details_div td,
.catalog_description > table > tbody > tr > td { padding: 10px; }
.sc_category_item .details_div h3:first-child,
.sc_category_item_hover .details_div h3:first-child,
.catalog_description > table > tbody > tr > td > h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
html[data-doctype=true] tr.header { background: transparent; }
html[data-doctype=true] div.sc_category_item, html[data-doctype=true] div.sc_category_item_hover { padding: 20px 0 !important; }
html[data-doctype=true] .sc_category_item_left { padding-right: 20px; }

/* Catalog Shopping Cart Container */
#cartContent { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; }
.sc_cat_set_window, .sc_cart_window { margin: 0; border: 0 none; }
.sc_cart_window { min-width: 175px; width: 100% !important; }

/* Catalog Shopping Cart Top */
#cartContent_header { padding-bottom: 10px; }
#cart { padding: 0 10px; border: 0 none; }
#adder { border: 1px solid #CCC; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px; }
#qty { margin-top: 10px; }

/* Catalog Shopping Cart Bottom */
.sc_cart_subtotal_row td { padding-top: 10px; }

/* Live Feed */

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>This script loads the layout/bootstrapping for the Branded CMS template as well as any custom functionality using various JS libraries.</description><global>false</global><name>branded-cms-init</name><script><![CDATA[// This script loads the layout/bootstrapping for the Branded CMS template as well as any custom functionality using various JS libraries.
var jquery;

( function( $j ) {
	var requireConfig = {
			deps : [ 'jquery', 'brandedlayout' ],

			paths : {
				'jquery' : '/branded-jquery.min.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'bootstrap' : '/bootstrap.min.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'underscore' : '/branded-lodash.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'backbone' : '/branded-backbone.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'infinitescroll' : '/jquery.infinitescroll.min.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'brandedlayout' : '/branded-cms-layout.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'brandedgethelp' : '/branded-get-help.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'brandedtypeaheadbundle' : '/branded-typeahead.bundle.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'brandedtypeaheadsetup' : '/branded-typeahead-setup.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'brandedknowledgebase' : '/branded-knowledgebase.jsdbx?dummy_ext=',
				'brandedcatalog' : '/branded-catalog.jsdbx?dummy_ext='
			},

			shim : {
				'brandedlayout' : { 'deps' : [ 'jquery' ] },
				'bootstrap' : { 'deps' : [ 'jquery' ] }
			},

			callback : function() {
				jquery = jQuery.noConflict();
			}
		};

	$j.getScript( '/require.jsdbx' ).done( function() {
		var pathJsMap = [
				{ path : 'get_help.do', require : 'brandedgethelp' },
				{ path : 'knowledgebase.do', require : 'brandedknowledgebase' },
				{ path : 'requestsomething.do', require : 'brandedcatalog' }
			],
			i;

		requirejs.config( requireConfig );

		for ( i = 0; i < pathJsMap.length; i++ ) {
			if ( window.location.pathname.indexOf( pathJsMap[ i ].path ) !== -1 ) {
				requirejs( [ pathJsMap[ i ].require ], function() {} );
				i = pathJsMap.length;
			}
		}
	} );
} )( jQuery );
]]></script><script_name/><sys_class_name>sys_ui_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-02-09 22:33:32</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>ce7625079b0231003fe61c7606549830</sys_id><sys_mod_count>36</sys_mod_count><sys_name>branded-cms-init</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ui_script_ce7625079b0231003fe61c7606549830</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-23 04:53:55</sys_updated_on><use_scoped_format>false</use_scoped_format></sys_ui_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: content_block_programmatic_c100bfe69b0331003fe61c76065498ab
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_block_programmatic"><content_block_programmatic action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><category>general</category><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><frame/><logged_on>false</logged_on><name>Branded CMS Get Help IFrame Loader</name><programmatic_content><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">

<g:evaluate jelly="true">
	var department = RP.getParameterValue( 'department' ).toLowerCase(),
		menuGr = new GlideRecord( 'menu_section' ),
		supportFrame = new GlideRecord( 'content_block_iframe' ),
		supportIdMap = [
			{ department : 'it', sysId : '23bc1ce84db0b10062c55dc1f2a64e2a' },
			{ department : 'facilities', sysId : 'a9700d204df0b10062c55dc1f2a64e38' },
			{ department : 'finance', sysId : '0f39f2164f227100c163e321a310c74d' },
			{ department : 'hr', sysId : 'b4a9ac6c4db0b10062c55dc1f2a64ee2' },
			{ department : 'legal', sysId : '88b0cb564f227100c163e321a310c7cb' },
			{ department : 'marketing', sysId : '467347964f227100c163e321a310c799' }
		],
		supportIds = [],
		supportMenuUrls = {},
		supportUrl,
		i;

	for ( i = 0; i < supportIdMap.length; i++ ) {
		supportIds.push( supportIdMap[ i ].sysId );
	}

	menuGr.addQuery( 'content_block_menu', 'IN', supportIds.join( ',' ) );
	menuGr.orderBy( 'order' );
	menuGr.query();

	while ( menuGr.next() ) {
		if ( typeof supportMenuUrls[ menuGr.content_block_menu ] === 'undefined' ) {
			supportMenuUrls[ menuGr.content_block_menu ] = [];
		}

		supportMenuUrls[ menuGr.content_block_menu ].push( menuGr.url.toString() );
	}

	if ( department ) {
		for ( i = 0; i < supportIdMap.length; i++ ) {
			if ( department == supportIdMap[ i ].department ) {
				supportUrl = supportMenuUrls[ supportIdMap[ i ].sysId ][ 0 ]
				i = supportIdMap.length;
			}
		}
	} else {
		supportUrl = supportMenuUrls[ supportIdMap[ 0 ].sysId ][ 0 ];
	}

	supportFrame.initialize();
	supportFrame.frame_name = 'support_frame';
	supportFrame.url = supportUrl;
	supportFrame.sizing = 'expand';
	supportFrame.putCurrent();
</g:evaluate>
<g:render_content_block_iframe />
<g:evaluate>
	supportFrame.popCurrent();
</g:evaluate>

</j:jelly>
]]></programmatic_content><sys_class_name>content_block_programmatic</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-03-30 12:20:06</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>c100bfe69b0331003fe61c76065498ab</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Get Help IFrame Loader</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_block_programmatic_c100bfe69b0331003fe61c76065498ab</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-03-30 12:20:06</sys_updated_on><two_phase>false</two_phase></content_block_programmatic></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS Custom Theme</name><style>/*********
Here you can apply custom color theming to the Branded CMS Template.

For a nice way to experiment with colors, see https://color.adobe.com/create/color-wheel/. An even simpler color picker can be found at http://colorpicker.com/.
*********/

/* General Link Styles */
a {
	color: #337AB7;
	transition: color 200ms;
}
a:hover { /* When the mouse is hovering over a link */
	color: #278EFC;
	text-decoration: none; /* removes underlines when hovering */
}
a:active, a:focus { /* When the mouse is in the middle of a click or just after a link has been clicked */
	color: #337AB7;
	text-decoration: underline;
}

.cms_header_bottom_menu a { /* Main Menu Links */
	color: #777;
}
.cms_header_bottom_menu a:hover {
	color: #337AB7;
}</style><sys_class_name>content_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>kai.yao</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-12-02 19:46:55</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>b1c72538b134310062c560307f64330f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>21</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Custom Theme</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_css_b1c72538b134310062c560307f64330f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-02-23 08:16:32</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css></record_update>
